window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ethan didn’t believe in magical swords until one transported him to a fantasy world. </p> <p>A world with monsters, martial arts guilds, and elemental powers beyond imagining. </p> <p>In fact, it’s almost like he died and went to heaven. If heaven contained rivals bent on killing him, elf tutors who want to bed him, and a feisty spearmaiden with something to prove. </p> <p><i>Contains harem elements.</i></p>"; 
